headline: Baxter to Present at TD Cowen 45th Annual Health Care Conference
summary: DEERFIELD, Ill., February 18, 2025--Baxter International Inc. (NYSE:BAX), a global medtech leader, will present at the TD Cowen 45th Annual Health Care Conference on Wednesday, March 5, 2025. Joel Grade, Baxter’s chief financial officer, is scheduled to present at 1:10 p.m. Eastern Time.
